description:
Does God kill? Does He pour out His “wrath” on those who upset Him? Or does He withdraw His life-giving power? Walter Veith addresses these questions in this Bible study. Walter also addresses the fact that God has a standard of morality and a standard of character that is beyond our comprehension and capacity. Listen to Walter explain about Biblical examples of God’s mighty power. Walter also discusses God’s process of probation and His process of executing judgment using Scriptural references. 

For more please visit: http://amazingdiscoveries.tv/c/95/Bible Answers/
